WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
Pre-Op: PPE on. Forks down. Brake set.

00:03.000 --> 00:07.000
Do a clean 8-point check before you roll.

00:07.000 --> 00:11.000
Hard hat, safety vest, safety glasses - always.

00:11.000 --> 00:15.000
Parking brake engaged before you start inspection.

00:15.000 --> 00:19.000
Forks completely lowered to the floor.

00:19.000 --> 00:23.000
Check for leaks, damage, or missing parts.

00:23.000 --> 00:27.000
Data plate readable? Controls working? You're good to go.
